  <refentry id="function.exp">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>exp</refname>
    <refpurpose><constant>e</constant>(자연로그 밑)의 승수를 계산합니다.</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>설명</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>float</type><methodname>exp</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>float</type><parameter>arg</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     <constant>e</constant>의 <parameter>arg</parameter>승을 반환합니다.
    </para>
    <note>
     <para>
      'e'는 자연로그의 밑으로, 약 2.718282입니다.
     </para>
    </note>
    <para>
     <example>
      <title><function>exp</function> 예제</title>
      <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
echo exp(12) . "\n";
echo exp(5.7);
?>
]]>
      </programlisting>
      <para>
       위 예제의 출력은:
      </para>
      <screen>
<![CDATA[
1.6257E+005
298.87
]]>
      </screen>
     </example>
    </para>
    <para>
     참고: <function>log</function>, <function>pow</function>.
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

